For those of you attending the Joint US Sections Combustion Institute
meeting in Chicago...

I will bring a couple of Cantera Windows installation CDs, so if you
are bringing a laptop and want to install Cantera on it, look for me
or stop by my poster (in the 'Fuel Cells' section) Tuesday afternoon.
You can also leave a message for me at the Essix Inn, starting Sunday.
